%%{init: {"sequence": {"messageMargin": 64, "noteMargin": 24, "boxMargin": 18, "wrap": true}}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User as Proxy Voter
    participant App as Voting App
    participant Server as API Server
    participant DB as Database

    User->>App: Enter represented voter details
    App->>App: Encrypt payload
    App->>Server: POST /api/voter/lookup-for-auth (represented)
    Server->>DB: Find represented voter by SDI
    DB-->>Server: Represented voter record
    Server-->>App: Represented voterId

    User->>App: Enter proxy voter details
    App->>App: Encrypt payload
    App->>Server: POST /api/voter/lookup-for-auth (proxy)
    Server->>DB: Find proxy voter by SDI
    DB-->>Server: Proxy voter record
    Server-->>App: Proxy voterId

    App->>App: Encrypt authorization payload
    App->>Server: POST /api/voter/validate-proxy-authorization
    Server->>DB: Load both voters + check proxy SDI match
    DB-->>Server: Authorization data

    alt Proxy is authorized
        Server-->>App: 200 OK
        App-->>User: Proxy authorized
        Note over App,Server: Continues to voter-auth-dataflow-only using proxy fingerprint
    else Not authorized or already voted
        Server-->>App: 400 authorization failed
        App-->>User: Stop and request official help
    end
